title: The Ballpark | Extra Innings: Professor Ayse Zarakol on the future of Liberal Internationalism and the War in Ukraine
itunes:author: Professor Ayse Zarakol, Chris Gilson, Mohid Rehman Malik
description: Contributor(s): Professor Ayse Zarakol, Chris Gilson, Mohid Rehman Malik | They also discuss what the rise of non-Western powers that have not fully adhered to Liberal Internationalism suggests about the future of this American-led system. This Extra Inning was produced by Chris Gilson, Mohid Malik, and Emmanuel Olugbenga.
